                        <div class="row">
                            <p class="paragraph">Acetone is an organic compound with the formula (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CO. It is the simplest and smallest Ketone (>c=o). It is a colorless, highly volatile, and flammable liquid with a characteristic pungent odor.</p>
