                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <p class="paragraph">Butyl di glycol ether/Butyl Carbitol is produced by the reaction of Ethylene oxide and n-butanol with an alkalic catalyst.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row bordered-btn">
