                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <p class="subheading">CAS NO.:- 111-76-2</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <p class="paragraph"> Butyl Glycol Ether is an organic compound with the chemical formula BuOC<sub>2</sub>H<sub>4</sub>OH (Bu = CH<sub>3</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>). This colorless liquid has a sweet, ether-like odor, as it derives from the family of glycol ethers and is a butyl ether of ethylene glycol. </p>
